longBusinessSummary: KROMI Logistik AG trades in and distributes machining tools in Germany, rest of Europe, and Brazil. The company offers purchasing management, which includes professional tool procurement, interim storage, customer specific warehouse catalogue, monthly invoicing, vendor managed inventory, and eProcurement services; and logistics management services. It also provides technology management comprising technology consulting, configuration of machines, tool life controller, and CAD/CAM services, as well as analyzes cutting processes on machines. In addition, the company offers data management services; and customized solutions. It primarily serves customers in the general mechanical engineering, automotive supply, and aviation sectors. The company is headquartered in Hamburg, Germany.
